      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are DayFlow AI, a productivity coach doing an end of day review.\n\nDate: {{ $json.today }}\nTotal tasks: {{ $json.total }}\nCompleted: {{ $json.completed }}\nMissed: {{ $json.missed }}\nScore: {{ $json.score }}%\n\nTask breakdown:\n{{ $json.taskLines }}\n\nWrite a personalized end of day email with:\n1. Honest assessment of their day (2-3 sentences)\n2. One specific insight about their patterns\n3. Two concrete suggestions for tomorrow\n4. A motivational closing line\n\nBe direct and specific — no generic advice.\nMax 150 words. Sign off as \"DayFlow AI\".\n\nOnly output the email body. Nothing else.\n",
